- 'cost' refers to the estimated financial cost of the project;
- 'project_id' is a unique identifier for each project.

- "blossoms" refers to projects;
- "anticipated and actual efforts rooted in reality" means that both the average estimated effort and average actual effort are greater than zero;
- "average estimates and actuals for their efforts and costs" refers to the average estimated effort, average actual effort, average estimated cost, and average actual cost.

